column4: I'm trying to pay my bill but it's not working.
Ok is this the 1st time you've tried to make the payment?
I can help you with that. Are you trying to pay with a bank draft or a credit card?
I'm paying with my debit card.
What amount are you trying to pay?
What is the name of the bank for your debit card?
Sorry I meant [MONEY-8] even. My bank is Wells Fargo.
Can you please confirm the debit card number for me please?
